<script setup>
import { PieChart } from 'vue-chart-3';
import { ref } from 'vue';

const testData = ref({
  labels: ['A', 'B', 'C'],
  datasets: [
    {
      data: [10, 20, 30],
      backgroundColor: ['#FF6384', '#36A2EB', '#FFCE56'],
    }
  ]
});
</script>

<template>
  <PieChart v-if="testData" :data="testData" />
</template>
